pos_examples: Now, communicate image data from rover frame_9 at waypoint kumquat_8 to lander rain at waypoint kumquat regarding objective object_260 in mode teddy.
(communicate_image_data frame_9 rain object_260 teddy kumquat_8 kumquat)
Once you are done, please sample soil at waypoint kumquat using rover roof_11 and store in store screen.

First, take image of objective yew at waypoint kumquat_8 using camera dress_red in mode bastion on rover frame_9 and then calibrate rover frame_9 with camera socket on objective object_260 at waypoint kumquat_8.

(take_image frame_9 kumquat_8 yew dress_red bastion)
(calibrate frame_9 socket object_260 kumquat_8)
The next step is to drop rover frame_9 from store fire.
